    <div class="bp-container">
      <div class="bp-reveal">
        <p class="bp-section-label">Inside the Book</p>
        <h2 class="bp-section-heading">75 patterns. Use only what you need.</h2>
        <p class="bp-inside-intro">You could read this cover-to-cover, but it&rsquo;s better thought of as a cookbook for organizations&mdash;75 specific moves for people who run teams and systems. Redesign a team, rewrite a role, rethink a decision path, strip out pointless work. Keep it on your desk, open it when something&rsquo;s stuck, and use the pattern that fits.</p>
      </div>

